Class Analyzer

java.lang.Object
  xtc.tree.Visitor
      xtc.lang.jeannie.Analyzer

public final class Analyzer
extends Visitor

A visitor that constructs a symbol table for a Jeannie file. Assumes that the AST has been simplified with jeannie.AstSimplifier.
